<HEADLINE> Slater at Reopening of Radio City </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	NEW YORK (AP) -- Christian Slater had a personal reason to show  
up at the grand reopening of Radio City Music Hall. 
</P>
<P>
	``I performed here as a child,'' Slater said as he was rushed  
past the media and into the renovated theater Monday evening. 
``It's a place of history and it's a cornerstone of New York City. 
It's great it's restored.'' 
</P>
<P>
