Internet company said Microsoft Corp. co-founder Paul Allen, will 
invest $1.65 billion to help it enlarge its network. Vulcan already 
owns 4.5 percent of RCN. The new investment boosts its stake to 
27.4 percent. 

</P>
<P>
	Pediatrix Medical Group, down 3 11/16 at 9 7/8  
</P>
<P>
	The Fort Lauderdale, Fla.-based company which manages  
pediatrician offices said earnings for the third quarter will fall 
far short of forecasts. The company blamed the shortfall on 
treating healthier patients, which hurt billings. 

</P>
